headline: Q4 Home Furnishings Earnings: Purple (NASDAQ:PRPL) Earns Top Marks
summary: The end of the earnings season is always a good time to take a step back and see who shined (and who not so much). Let’s take a look at how home furnishings stocks fared in Q4, starting with Purple (NASDAQ:PRPL).
